data.meta_description: Kevin Earl Federline (born March 21, 1978) is an English-American/Irish-American/Scottish-American/German-American/Italian-American dancer. Kevin was 1 when Chris was born. Kevin was 8 when Julie & Mike got divorced. Kevin was 12 when Kurtis was born. Kevin was 22 when he & Shar began dating...
